---
description: How to add and use Python dependencies
globs: 
alwaysApply: true
---
- for Python dependencies the uv package manager is used
- for new production dependencies use `uv add <package-name>`
- for new development dependencies use `uv add --dev <package-name>`
- Python CLI tools shall be called within uv's virtual environment, e.g. `ev run python main.py`
